1
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:16,730
Sweetie.

2
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:18,760
How about

3
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,760
you go play with the kids for a while?

4
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:21,640
No.

5
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,480
I want to go home and watch cartoons.

6
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,240
What cartoons?

7
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:25,170
You'll go blind.

8
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,200
Oh.

9
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:27,720
Come on.

10
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:28,280
Be good.

11
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,120
Look,

12
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,200
they are all playing over there.

13
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:30,680
You go play too,

14
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,160
okay?

15
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,180
Do you want to play too?

16
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:42,880
Okay.

17
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,600
Then you

18
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,880
line up at the back.

19
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:45,520
Hold on.

20
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,570
Here comes another kid.

21
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,010
What am I supposed to say to you?

22
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,980
I always thought you were a sensible person.

23
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,600
Kids don't lie.

24
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,440
You knew exactly where Liu Jiang was,

25
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,700
but you didn't tell us.

26
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:03,120
You even arranged for the child to talk to him.

27
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:05,720
You've been in contact all along, haven't you?

28
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,180
Do you know you've committed a crime?

29
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:13,960
The child is so young.

30
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,160
What do you expect her to do in the future?

31
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,490
How is she going to live?

32
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,810
We are all doing this for your own good.

33
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:24,170
Think it through yourself.

34
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:36,940
Master, I found it.

35
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,440
Liu Jiang made an appointment with his wife

36
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,680
to communicate secretly online.

37
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,760
He is currently hiding in Lianshui County.

38
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,090
I'll go there right away

39
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,520
and bring Liu Jiang back.

40
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:45,960
Also,

41
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,000
be safe.

42
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,520
Rest assured.

43
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,200
This time I will definitely obey orders,

44
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:50,880
follow commands,

45
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,680
and guarantee mission success.

46
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:56,240
I'm heading there right now.

47
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,160
Guan Jing.

48
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,160
Found it.

49
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:08,820
Right here.

50
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:11,280
She was cremated here in 2005.

51
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,930
The cause of death is...

52
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,900
Heart disease.

53
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,680
Please make a copy

54
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,200
of the death certificate for me.

55
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:20,680
Okay.

56
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,680
The hospital has no hospitalization record,

57
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,680
so why does the death certificate

58
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,680
have the hospital's official seal?

59
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,800
This death certificate is fake.

60
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,860
We didn't issue it.

61
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,730
Are you sure?

62
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:41,120
The security thread doesn't match our official seal.

63
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,250
Captain Sun.

64
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,680
I found Wang Qiang's car.

65
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,680
Because he needed money,

66
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,640
he sold it to a used car dealer.

67
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,880
I found out and stopped it,

68
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:37,960
and sent it to Sister Zhen for inspection.

69
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,159
The report just came out.

70
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:39,600
Here.

71
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:40,760
It has been confirmed.

72
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,960
The bloodstains in the trunk

73
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:42,480
belong to

74
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,740
Lu Wei and Pan Shuping.

75
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,040
Oh, right.

76
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,900
I've updated Brother Yan and the others on this.

77
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:54,840
Hello?

78
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:57,720
Got it.

79
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,440
We've found Wang Qiang's whereabouts.

80
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,120
Yesterday afternoon,

81
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,000
he headed towards Donglin.

82
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,920
Take your men to catch him.

83
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,320
Okay.

84
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,680
Brother Peng.

85
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,920
Through the online contact given by Liu Jiang's wife,

86
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:17,320
we tracked down Liu Jiang's current cell phone number.

87
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,240
Through triangulation,

88
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,600
we located him at 23 Anning Road, Lianshui County.

89
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,660
It's a small motel.

90
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,520
I did it.

91
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,210
I can pay for it with my life.

92
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,480
Pay with your life?

93
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,440
Two lives.

94
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,840
How are you going to pay for them?

95
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,680
Two?

96
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,600
My life only pays for Shuping.

97
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,960
That guy surnamed Lv deserved to die.

98
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,059
Now that you've caught me,

99
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,650
and I won't live anyway,

100
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:36,600
I confess.

101
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:40,960
Tell me.

102
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,640
Why did you kill them?

103
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,370
Did you hold a grudge against them?

104
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:47,400
Actually,

105
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:49,600
that guy surnamed Lu didn't have to die.

106
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,610
We agreed on three days,

107
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,920
but he just had to come back at that time.

108
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,920
Shuping originally promised me

109
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:58,160
that she would break up with Lu Wei when he came back.

110
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,420
But I didn't expect it.

111
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:02,130
I think Shuping still cared about me a lot.

112
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,680
She said, "You're alone in the shop,

113
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:06,140
with no one to cook for you,

114
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,880
and it's uncomfortable to sleep there.

115
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:11,140
Come back and live together from now on."

116
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,320
But that night,

117
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:15,000
when we were... you know,

118
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,840
Lu suddenly came back.

119
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,200
He hit me without a word.

120
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:23,160
I didn't fight back at first.

121
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,210
He insisted that

122
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,720
Shuping choose between him and me.

123
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,060
Shuping said nothing,

124
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,800
so he tried to hit her.

125
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,000
How could I stand for that?

126
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,930
Then let's do it.

127
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:33,680
I slipped

128
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,420
and hit him on the head with the knife.

129
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:37,760
And he died.

130
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:54,770
Why did you dismember the body?

131
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,050
Was it to destroy the evidence?

132
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:01,960
No.

133
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,200
Lü Wei died.

134
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:09,120
He glared at me with those eyes.

135
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,240
It freaked me out.

136
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,120
I just cut

137
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,360
his head off.

138
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,200
Then why did Pan Shuping die too?

139
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:26,200
I said we could just bury Lü Wei somewhere.

140
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,440
We could move to another city,

141
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,880
find a new place, and live a good life.

142
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:29,960
Wouldn't that be nice?

143
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,020
But what happened?

144
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,440
Shuping insisted that I turn myself in.

145
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,560
Just because of that?

146
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:36,040
Shuping insisted on calling the police.

147
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:37,840
She wanted to send me to prison herself.

148
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,560
That hurt more than killing me.

149
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:41,040
I really misjudged her.

150
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,520
She didn't love me.

151
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:16,160
So I killed her.

152
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,320
But...

153
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,600
Having said that,

154
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:22,840
that Lü Wei...

155
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,480
he truly deserved to die.

156
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:26,880
He hit and killed someone with his car a while ago.

157
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,080
You know that, right?

158
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,400
After that person died,

159
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:31,130
he gave Shuping a diamond ring.

160
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,210
A pretty big one.

161
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,000
He's just a truck driver.

162
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,680
How could he afford that?

163
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:37,680
He must have done something bad.

164
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,100
I consider this

165
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:42,560
ridding the people of an evil.

166
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:38,170
Are we almost there?

167
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,130
Yes, right here.

168
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,560
Hello.

169
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,160
Who is the boss?

170
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,920
Are you looking for a room?

171
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,920
We are the police.

172
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,360
Please cooperate with our work.

173
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,400
Do you have a back door here?

174
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:09,060
We don't have a back door here.

175
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,840
Have you seen

176
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,570
this person?

177
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:14,320
This person,

178
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,080
looks familiar.

179
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:15,880
I've seen him.

180
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:03,360
Right here.

181
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,220
The third room.

182
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:20,060
Housekeeping.

183
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:28,210
Is anyone there?

184
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:29,400
Housekeeping.

185
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,010
Split up.

186
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:56,480
Okay.

187
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:36,800
Wait for me.

188
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,360
Catch me.

189
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,680
Let me play with it for a while.

190
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:41,520
No.

191
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,200
This is mine.

192
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:44,560
Catch me,

193
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:46,020
and I'll give it to you.

194
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:52,400
Wait.

195
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:53,680
No.

196
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,800
Just let me play for a bit.

197
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,560
Just for a while, then.

198
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:58,080
Okay.

199
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:58,860
Here you go.

200
00:15:58,880 --> 00:15:59,520
Thank you.

201
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:06,880
You again.

202
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:07,520
Stop!

203
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:10,720
Liu Jiang, don't run!

204
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:56,880
Jia Peng.

205
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:16,770
Jia Peng.

206
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:17,800
Jia Peng.

207
00:17:18,359 --> 00:17:18,890
Jia Peng.

208
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:21,170
Jia Peng.

209
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:23,010
Jia Peng.

210
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,480
Hold on.

211
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:26,960
You'll be fine.

212
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:28,000
Lin Xiao.

213
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:33,840
Am I going to die?

214
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:35,160
No.

215
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:36,160
You won't.

216
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:36,760
It's okay.

217
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:38,000
It's okay. I'll take...

218
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,060
I'll take you back.

219
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,340
You'll be fine.

220
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:41,520
Hold on, Jia Peng.

221
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:43,560
Hold on.

222
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:44,640
Hold on.

223
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:49,760
Lin Xiao.

224
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:52,120
Tell my master,

225
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:55,840
this time,

226
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:59,320
I followed his orders.

227
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:04,120
I obeyed the command.

228
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,000
Jia Peng.

229
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:22,480
Jia Peng.

230
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:24,960
Jia Peng.

231
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,160
Jia Peng.
